        {
          "text": "This book is not about one person. "
        }
      ],
      "sourceParagraph": 72
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "runs": [
        {
          "text": "It is not about one relationship. "
        }
      ],
      "sourceParagraph": 73
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "runs": [
        {
          "text": "It is not about one ending. "
        }
      ],
      "sourceParagraph": 74
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "runs": [
        {
          "text": "It is about the silent psychological shifts that happen "
        }
      ],
      "sourceParagraph": 75
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "runs": [
        {
          "text": "inside people when attachment, distance, expectations, "
        }
